name: Venus after Csaky
description:
NFT counterpart of a physical sculpture - 24x24x78cm, 3D printed PLA plastic 🤖

Sculpted in VR us and 3D printed at the same scale as a found object garden statue of Venus de Milo.

After Csaky refers to Joseph Csaky, the cubist sculptor who made abstracted sculptures of the human form. Thinking about historical connections, creating and collapsing forms with new technologies, replicating a replica of a replica.
